    Given a file named "main.coel" with:
    """
    (write (match {"foo" {42 2049} "bar" {"This" "Matched!"}}
      [[..foo] ["This" "is" "not" "Matched!"]] "Not matched..."
      {"foo" {42 2050} "bar" {"This" "Matched!"}} "Not matched..."
